parameters:
But, it's all thanks to President Waltin, for
creating a new smoking area for us.

Really, lately us smokers have been feeling quite
uncomfortable...

Hahaha! Even so, what a ridiculous ashtray, it's
hilarious.

Esuka, who was captured by the Imperial Army, had
been severed from the head and remodeled into an
ashtray.

Gyahahaha! This is your punishment for opposing
us, make sure you reflect on it, okay?

If you work hard, you'll be returned to your
original form, right? Keep it up~

Well, time to get back to work. I have to go
around and capture your comrades after all.

Hahaha! This time, the resistance didn't put up
much of a fight. They were begging for their
lives.

As expected, after several months, the response
has gotten worse.

Come on, if you scream louder, someone might come
to help you, you know?

It's a shame that you have such weak comrades,
isn't it?
Hahaha! Well, time to get back to work.

Phew~ I'm tired, I'm tired. A smoke after work is
exceptional!
But where did this one's body go?
Oh, it seems like the officers are not around...!

Hmph! You've been causing such a ruckus, because
of you my bonus got cut, didn't it?
Whoa! Experience the wrath of the weak...!
Hehehe...! Make sure you reflect on this!

Ugh... Again? Seriously, make sure to clean up
properly...
